## Phase 1 Test Requirements (VIGIL)

12 tests total — 9 MUST + 3 SHOULD (test file name: canonical `.openclaw/workspace/tests/`,
ANVIL picks either `test_a5_confidence.py` or `test_micro_gate_confidence.py` — be consistent):

- 7 per-key confidence tests (one per map entry) — 4 MUST + 3 SHOULD (low-risk keys as SHOULD)
- `test_explicit_extractor_confidence_preserved` — explicit `ext.confidence=0.73` stays 0.73 (MUST)
- `test_unknown_method_gets_080` — unknown `extraction_method` falls back to 0.80 (MUST)
- `test_missing_method_gets_080` — missing `extraction_method` key → 0.80 (MUST)
- `test_confidence_gt1_normalization_unchanged` — 9.0 still normalizes to 0.9 (MUST)
- `test_explicit_high_confidence_preserved` — explicit 0.95 preserved through the flow (MUST)
